      <title>Re: Augments - BiC, Circle of Drakes??</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=TNZ&amp;message.id=245937#M245937</link>
      <description>&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; BIC = Breakdown in Communications. This is a full scale 14 quests in its own, requiring a lot of rare drops and in cases after quest 7, raid support. It is carried through-out every zone in gates of discord. It is probobly without a doubt the longest quest in the game currently. The rare drops have been adjusted since I did it so I hear its not "as" bad anymore, but here is the melee version of the last augment it Rewards you with. There are 14 parts to the quest starting from low scale events/farming in qinimi to the boss of Gates himself Tunat Muram.&lt;br&gt;-&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&#xD;
  Black Gemstone Of Pain&#xD;
  &#xD;
  &#xD;
  &#xD;
  MAGIC ITEM  LORE ITEM  NO TRADE  AUGMENTATION&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Augmentation type: All slot types&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Slot: HEAD FACE EAR NECK SHOULDERS ARMS BACK WRIST RANGE HANDS PRIMARY SECONDARY FINGER CHEST LEGS FEET WAIST&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
AC: 18&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
STR: +20  DEX: +20  STA: +20  AGI: +20  HP: +200  ENDUR: +150&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
SV FIRE: +18  SV DISEASE: +18  SV COLD: +18  SV MAGIC: +18  SV POISON: +18&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Regeneration: +4  &lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Required level of 65.&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
WT: 0.0  Size: TINY&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Class: WAR MNK ROG BER&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Race: ALL except ERU HIE Shroud&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;-&lt;br&gt;The circle of drakes is a 24 man nest event that takes around 15 minutes and can most likely be done by Qvic level guilds. It has 2 augs for completeing the short event as long as some other rewards. It is on a 3 day respawn timer and gives 1 loot per run.&lt;br&gt;-&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&#xD;
  Disc of the Dragon Kind&#xD;
  &#xD;
  &#xD;
  &#xD;
  MAGIC ITEM  LORE ITEM  NO TRADE  AUGMENTATION&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Augmentation type: 7 8 &lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Slot: HEAD FACE EAR NECK SHOULDERS ARMS BACK WRIST RANGE HANDS PRIMARY SECONDARY FINGER CHEST LEGS FEET WAIST&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
HP: +165&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Required level of 70.&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
WT: 0.0  Size: TINY&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Class: ALL&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Race: ALL&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Item Information:&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
You must use the solvent &lt;a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=47018" target=_blank&gt;Class XVIII Augmentation Distiller&lt;/a&gt; to remove this augment safely.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;and, &lt;br&gt;&#xD;
  Ore of the Nest&#xD;
  &#xD;
  &#xD;
  &#xD;
  MAGIC ITEM  LORE ITEM  NO TRADE  AUGMENTATION&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Augmentation type: 7 8 &lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Slot: HEAD FACE EAR NECK SHOULDERS ARMS BACK WRIST RANGE HANDS PRIMARY SECONDARY FINGER CHEST LEGS FEET WAIST&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
HP: +90  MANA: +75  ENDUR: +75&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Shielding: +4%  &lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Required level of 70.&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
WT: 0.0  Size: TINY&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Class: ALL&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Race: ALL&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
&lt;br&gt;Item Information:&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
You must use the solvent &lt;a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=47018" target=_blank&gt;Class XVIII Augmentation Distiller&lt;/a&gt; to remove this augment safely.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
