      <title>Re: Augments - BiC, Circle of Drakes??</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=TNZ&amp;message.id=245872#M245872</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;bic is shorthand for Breakdown in Communications.&amp;nbsp; An insanely long quest going through various GoD zones.&amp;nbsp; Expect to be 65 at a MINIMUM, and with a strong raiding guild to complete this one.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;The Circle of Drakes is a task you get from either the good or evil camps in Dragons of Norrath.&amp;nbsp; It is a 24 person Max event, very fun, and also requires a decent guild to win the event.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Hope that helps&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
